	<h3>Map Grid</h3>
	This following demonstrates generating a <code>Grid</code> based on an array of <code>java.util.Map</code> instances.
	The example adds <code>MapPropertyConduit</code> instances to an initially empty <code>BeanModel</code> (based on <code>java.lang.Object</code>)
	
	<h3>Demo</h3>
	<t:grid source="people" model="peopleModel" />

